title: Hungary partners Ghana FA to develop youth football
text:
Sports News | 14 October 2015 21:10 CET Hungary partners Ghana FA to develop youth football - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Hungary has expressed its readiness to partner Ghana in the area of youth football, infrastructural development and to share experience on developing football academies.
